<div class="prose max-w-none p-6">
<h1 id="navigatie" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#navigatie" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Navigatie</h1><p>In dit hoofdstuk leer je wat meer over navigeren binnen .NET Maui. Je krijgt antwoord op de vragen:</p><ul><li>Hoe navigeer je met een knop naar een menuitem.</li><li>Hoe navigeer je naar een andere pagina met behulp van een knop?</li><li>Hoe geef je argumenten door aan een andere pagina?</li><li>Hoe navigeer je naar een andere pagina nadat je op een item in een CollectionView klikt (tap)?</li></ul><h2 id="navigatie-naar-een-menuitem" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#navigatie-naar-een-menuitem" aria-hidden="true">#</a> navigatie naar een menuitem</h2><p>Navigatie naar een pagina via een flyout-menu ken je reeds. Wil je echter, met een knop op een pagina, navigeren naar een andere pagina uit het Flyoutmenu dan moet je een route aanmaken in <code>AppShell.xaml</code>. (regels 4 en 8) Deze <strong>route</strong> zorgt ervoor dat de Shell correct kan navigeren naar de juiste pagina.</p><div class="language-xml line-numbers-mode" data-ext="xml"><pre class="language-xml"><code>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>ShellContent</span>
        <span class="token attr-name">Title</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">&quot;</span>Home<span class="token punctuation">&quot;</span></span>
        <span class="token attr-name">ContentTemplate</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">&quot;</span>{DataTemplate views:HomePage}<span class="token punctuation">&quot;</span></span>
        <span class="token attr-name">Route</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">&quot;</span>HomePage<span class="token punctuation">&quot;</span></span> <span class="token punctuation">/&gt;</span></span>
    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>ShellContent</span>
        <span class="token attr-name">Title</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">&quot;</span>Labels<span class="token punctuation">&quot;</span></span>
        <span class="token attr-name">ContentTemplate</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">&quot;</span>{DataTemplate views:LabelsPage}<span class="token punctuation">&quot;</span></span>
        <span class="token attr-name">Route</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">&quot;</span>LabelsPage<span class="token punctuation">&quot;</span></span> <span class="token punctuation">/&gt;</span></span>
</code></pre><div class="highlight-lines"><br><br><br><div class="highlight-line"> </div><br><br><br><div class="highlight-line"> </div></div><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Deze route kun je aanspreken in de code van een <em>[RelayCommand]</em>.</p><div class="language-csharp line-numbers-mode" data-ext="cs"><pre class="language-csharp"><code>    <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token attribute"><span class="token class-name">RelayCommand</span></span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>
    <span class="token keyword">private</span> <span class="token keyword">async</span> <span class="token return-type class-name"><span class="token keyword">void</span></span> <span class="token function">GoHome</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
    <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
        <span class="token keyword">await</span> Shell<span class="token punctuation">.</span>Current<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">GoToAsync</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&quot;../HomePage&quot;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ul><li><strong>Shell.Current</strong>: Verwijst naar de huidige instantie van de Shell, een onderdeel van de .NET MAUI Shell-architectuur die een manier biedt om pagina&#39;s te organiseren en te navigeren.</li><li><strong>GoToAsync</strong>: Een methode om asynchrone navigatie uit te voeren.</li><li><strong>&quot;../HomePage&quot;</strong>: De route waarnaar genavigeerd moet worden. Het &quot;../&quot;-gedeelte geeft aan dat er één niveau omhoog in de navigatiehiërarchie wordt bewogen.</li></ul><h2 id="navigatie-naar-een-pagina" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#navigatie-naar-een-pagina" aria-hidden="true">#</a> navigatie naar een pagina</h2><p>Niet elke pagina heeft een menuitem. Als je wil navigeren naar zo&#39;n pagina, moet je ook een route registreren, maar dat doe je in <code>AppShell.xaml.cs</code></p><div class="language-csharp line-numbers-mode" data-ext="cs"><pre class="language-csharp"><code><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">partial</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">AppShell</span> <span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token type-list"><span class="token class-name">Shell</span></span>
<span class="token punctuation">{</span>
	<span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token function">AppShell</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
	<span class="token punctuation">{</span>
		<span class="token function">InitializeComponent</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>

        Routing<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">RegisterRoute</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">nameof</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>HomePage<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">typeof</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token type-expression class-name">homePage</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="highlight-lines"><br><br><br><br><br><br><div class="highlight-line"> </div><br><br></div><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ul><li><strong>Routing.RegisterRoute(...)</strong>: Dit is de methode om een route te registreren in het routingmechanisme van een .NET MAUI-applicatie. Een &quot;route&quot; is een URL-patroon dat overeenkomt met een bepaalde pagina in de app.</li><li><strong>typeof(HomePage)</strong>: Het gebruik van typeof is nodig om het specifieke type van de doelpagina aan te geven.</li><li>De <strong>nameof</strong> operator zorgt ervoor dat je altijd de juiste naam van de pagina gebruikt, zelfs als je de naam van de klasse hernoemt. Dit helpt bij het vermijden van fouten door typefouten.</li></ul><p>Het <em>[RelayCommand]</em> ziet er nu als volgt uit:</p><div class="language-csharp line-numbers-mode" data-ext="cs"><pre class="language-csharp"><code>    <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token attribute"><span class="token class-name">RelayCommand</span></span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>
    <span class="token keyword">private</span> <span class="token keyword">async</span> <span class="token return-type class-name"><span class="token keyword">void</span></span> <span class="token function">GoHome</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
    <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
        <span class="token keyword">await</span> Shell<span class="token punctuation">.</span>Current<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">GoToAsync</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">nameof</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>HomePage<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="highlight-lines"><br><br><br><div class="highlight-line"> </div><br></div><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="argumenten-doorgeven-aan-een-andere-pagina" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#argumenten-doorgeven-aan-een-andere-pagina" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Argumenten doorgeven aan een andere pagina</h2><p>Op het moment dat je navigeert naar een andere pagina en gegevens wil meegeven als argument, maak je een <strong>Dictionary</strong> aan waar je alle objecten inplaatst.</p><p>In het onderstaande voorbeeld maak je een <em>[RelayCommand]</em> voor navigatie naar een <code>DetailsPage</code> en geef je een object <code>Werknemer</code> mee.</p><div class="language-csharp line-numbers-mode" data-ext="cs"><pre class="language-csharp"><code><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token attribute"><span class="token class-name">RelayCommand</span></span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>
<span class="token keyword">private</span> <span class="token keyword">async</span> <span class="token return-type class-name">Task</span> <span class="token function">GoToDetails</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token punctuation">{</span>
    <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>werknemer <span class="token operator">==</span> <span class="token keyword">null</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
        <span class="token keyword">return</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
    <span class="token keyword">await</span> Shell<span class="token punctuation">.</span>Current<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">GoToAsync</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">nameof</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>DetailsPage<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token boolean">true</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token constructor-invocation class-name">Dictionary<span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span><span class="token keyword">string</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">object</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>
        <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
            <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token string">&quot;Werknemer&quot;</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> werknemer <span class="token punctuation">}</span>
        <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><ul><li><strong>true</strong>: Dit zorgt ervoor dat de &quot;terugnavigatiegeschiedenis&quot; actief is zodat je terug naar de vorige pagina kunt.</li><li><strong>new Dictionary&lt;string, object&gt; { { &quot;Werknemer&quot;, werknemer } }</strong>: definieert een dictionary met gegevens die moeten worden doorgegeven naar de doelpagina. In dit geval wordt een object van het type &quot;Werknemer&quot; doorgegeven met de sleutel &quot;Werknemer&quot;, zodat de doelpagina de details van de werknemer kan weergeven.</li></ul><p>In deze <strong>Dictionary</strong> kun je ook meerdere argumenten opnemen. Hieronder vind je de algemene schrijfwijze voor een <strong>Dictionary</strong>:</p><div class="language-csharp line-numbers-mode" data-ext="cs"><pre class="language-csharp"><code>    <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token constructor-invocation class-name">Dictionary<span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span><span class="token keyword">string</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">object</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>
        <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token string">&quot;Titel1&quot;</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> Object1<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>
        <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token string">&quot;Titel2&quot;</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> Object2<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>
        <span class="token range operator">..</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>
    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>In het <code>DetailsViewModel</code> kun je de argumenten ophalen met het kenmerk <strong>[QueryProperty]</strong>.</p><div class="language-csharp line-numbers-mode" data-ext="cs"><pre class="language-csharp"><code>    <span class="token keyword">namespace</span> <span class="token namespace">MauiIntroductie<span class="token punctuation">.</span>ViewModels</span>
    <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
        <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token attribute"><span class="token class-name">QueryProperty</span><span class="token attribute-arguments"><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">nameof</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>Werknemer<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">&quot;Werknemer&quot;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></span></span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>
        <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">partial</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">DetailsViewModel</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token type-list"><span class="token class-name">BaseViewModel</span></span>
        <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
            <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token attribute"><span class="token class-name">ObservableProperty</span></span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>
            <span class="token class-name">Werknemer</span> werknemer<span class="token punctuation">;</span>

        <span class="token punctuation">}</span>
    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><blockquote><p>Let op! De parameters van de [QueryProperty] staan omgedraaid ten opzichte van de Dictionary. De algemene schrijfwijze is:</p></blockquote><div class="language-csharp line-numbers-mode" data-ext="cs"><pre class="language-csharp"><code>    <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token attribute"><span class="token class-name">QueryProperty</span><span class="token attribute-arguments"><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">nameof</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>Object1<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">&quot;Titel1&quot;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></span></span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>
    <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token attribute"><span class="token class-name">QueryProperty</span><span class="token attribute-arguments"><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">nameof</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>Object2<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">&quot;Titel2&quot;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></span></span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><blockquote><p>Opmerking! Het inladen van de argumenten gebeurt nà het uitvoeren van de constructor van je ViewModel. Wil je bv nog een controle uitvoeren of een bewerking uitvoeren van je argument, doe je dit in een <strong>onPropertyChanged</strong>.</p></blockquote><div class="language-csharp line-numbers-mode" data-ext="cs"><pre class="language-csharp"><code>    <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token attribute"><span class="token class-name">QueryProperty</span><span class="token attribute-arguments"><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">nameof</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>Werknemer<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">&quot;Werknemer&quot;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></span></span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>
    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">partial</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">DetailsViewModel</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token type-list"><span class="token class-name">BaseViewModel</span></span>
    <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
        <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token attribute"><span class="token class-name">ObservableProperty</span></span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>
        <span class="token class-name">Werknemer</span> werknemer<span class="token punctuation">;</span>

        <span class="token keyword">partial</span> <span class="token return-type class-name"><span class="token keyword">void</span></span> <span class="token function">OnWerknemerChanged</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token class-name">Werknemer</span> <span class="token keyword">value</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
        <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
            <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">value</span> <span class="token operator">!=</span> <span class="token keyword">null</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
            <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
                Shell<span class="token punctuation">.</span>Current<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">DisplayAlert</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&quot;Fout&quot;</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">&quot;De werknemer is niet correct geladen&quot;</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">&quot;Doorgaan&quot;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
            <span class="token punctuation">}</span>
        <span class="token punctuation">}</span>
    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="highlight-lines"><br><br><br><br><br><br><div class="highlight-line"> </div><div class="highlight-line"> </div><div class="highlight-line"> </div><div class="highlight-line"> </div><div class="highlight-line"> </div><div class="highlight-line"> </div><div class="highlight-line"> </div><br></div><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="navigatie-met-gesturerecognizers" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#navigatie-met-gesturerecognizers" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Navigatie met GestureRecognizers</h2><p>Hierboven staan de standaard navigatiemogelijkheden maar in de termen van MultiPlatform is het interessant om het ook te hebben over GestureRecognizers. Dit is een eigenschap van een control die herkent wat voor beweging of gebaar je uitvoert op de control. Zo kun je <em>tappen</em>, <em>swipen</em>, <em>drag-drop</em> of <em>pinchen</em>. Je voegt een GestureRecognizer toe in de xaml-code van je pagina.</p><p>Achter deze beweging programmeer je dan een methode met het kenmerk [RelayCommand] in je ViewModel.</p><p>Dit is een voorbeeld van een <strong>TapGestureRecognizer</strong> die de <code>DetailsPage</code> oproept als je op een werknemer <em>tapt</em>:</p><div class="language-csharp line-numbers-mode" data-ext="cs"><pre class="language-csharp"><code>        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">CollectionView</span> ItemsSource<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">&quot;{Binding Werknemers}&quot;</span> SelectedItem<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">&quot;{Binding Werknemer}&quot;</span> SelectionMode<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">&quot;Single&quot;</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span>
            <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>CollectionView<span class="token punctuation">.</span>Header<span class="token operator">&gt;</span>
                <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">Grid</span> ColumnDefinitions<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">&quot;*,*,*,*,*&quot;</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span>
                    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">Label</span> Text<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">&quot;Id&quot;</span> Grid<span class="token punctuation">.</span>Column<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">&quot;0&quot;</span> FontSize<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">&quot;Small&quot;</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span>
